」俾人扣易拎嘅表達組織分，二嚟見解論證吹水位多啲，唔多使用錄音資料，可以多啲發揮，盡量拎多啲分。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:15:42.000Z","msg":"唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一條問題係問卷三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T07:47:10.000Z","msg":"首尾段因應題目嘅格式、題材唔同，寫嘅嘢就會唔同，建議你上返hkeaa到睇下人地點做。<br />\n<br />\n過渡段都係每次唔同，但大概都係「以上便是本人對xx的一些整合，有鑑xx逐漸受到社會各界關注，故本人想作出一些aa和bb」(視乎題目見解論證問咩，最尾嗰句先寫咩)<br />\n<br />\nxx係個文章主題，eg上年嘅活化小學，xx就寫活化小學。<br />\naa, bb係個見解論證要你做咩，你就寫咩落去。<br />\n<br />\n利伸 耐無去做卷三，好多嘢都生疏曬，做個參考就算，有用你先拎去用"},{"pid":"039bdf974a745d2c9b57345f08c47353ba43d1c7","tid":589651,"uid":69217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b490ff33af32d18de0292a9bc1260177ab83031","tid":589651,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"361cca90139b0d52da42ada5e698c51e0196ab70","tid":589651,"uid":69217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2b43bf800b14f60a05dbb408094ef577ba2183b","tid":589651,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c7064c5ec780b888bbd75f18496c3b541c22861","tid":589651,"uid":69217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T17:25:56.000Z","msg":"試下睇下IG入面嘅作文心得分享post，睇下幫唔幫到你。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T18:36:15.000Z","msg":"睇了<br />\n咪即係上面你講個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁不如你作篇文sd過嚟，你就咁講，我都唔知你問題係邊，俾唔到針對性建議你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:09:25.000Z","msg":"Tg定ig方便啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b101be4baf4c98ce83483f9f3bfe8e947dda365","tid":589651,"uid":87563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0082f19e1b5b3df16ff1ee1c505d2fa31e6e88","tid":589651,"uid":69217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b490ff33af32d18de0292a9bc1260177ab83031","tid":589651,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"361cca90139b0d52da42ada5e698c51e0196ab70","tid":589651,"uid":69217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2b43bf800b14f60a05dbb408094ef577ba2183b","tid":589651,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T18:36:15.000Z","msg":"睇了<br />\n咪即係上面你講個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁不如你作篇文sd過嚟，你就咁講，我都唔知你問題係邊，俾唔到針對性建議你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:09:25.000Z","msg":"Tg定ig方便啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T13:43:02.000Z","msg":"tg"},{"pid":"bd2865a46fe2b77c7e3e2052e09676264b8fc86a","tid":589651,"uid":69217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T17:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac465e9a28d2822088401f0e768ce0aab48301d","tid":589651,"uid":63675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T20:19:18.000Z","msg":"幫推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都分享下自己心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只限記敘<br />\n利申卷2得5 overall 得3 學校miss一路都只係比我卷2 level3(校內試+mock)<br />\n<br />\n首先我自認文筆唔係好 亦無可能寫得出一篇5**既文 但有幾個技巧的確可以提升你篇文章帶比人既觀感 <br />\n<br />\n記敘文一般要求係有起承轉合 要突顯到高潮之餘 亦都不忘寫出一個正面既道理<br />\n首先 我會用天氣+擬聲做入題黎做入題 eg: 沙沙沙... 窗外一陣陣的狂風暴雨 不停拍打在窗戶上 夜闌人靜 躺在床上的我 回想起xxxx 我的心情仍是久久不能平復 即刻過去多年 我亦是未能釋懷 眶中的淚水 尤如外面的雨點 沒完沒了地流出來 <br />\n<br />\n大概係咁樣 老實講 寫到大概咁既intro 已經係可以吸引到mRker既注意<br />\n<br />\n去到中間 用200-300字精簡咁講出件事 用少少 對話 唔同既句式（排比 頂真 比喻etc.) 加一兩個成語<br />\n<br />\n高潮位就要仔細咁講個轉捩點/發生左咩事 令你有咁大轉變 成語 形容辭走唔甩 仲有少少句子eg 熱鍋上的螞蟻...等等都可以吸引到讀者既目光 用起碼350字係最基本<br />\n結尾多數分2段 第一段講件事既結果+一句反思<br />\n<br />\n第2段就講反思 亦即係昇華 吹噓下帶比你個樣野有幾珍貴 再講點應用喺生活上 2段加埋100+100字<br />\n呢個係大概既脈絡 原諒我打得有d hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望幫到你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即使文筆差 都可以靠呢d野修飾 文筆差絕對唔係致命傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最重要係開卷後唔好落筆 而係用10分鐘諗清楚邊條啱自己然後再諗個故仔出黎 係合理而不離題 再用多5分鐘去諗有咩野係同個幾隻字有關 連繫所有有關既野 呢個就係拎高分既精髓 呢部份真係最緊要 各位考生加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ccf9c7e01855dd6ac966efb601ed61d3d0dbb4","tid":589651,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T20:20:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都分享下自己心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只限記敘<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n希望你地唔會tldr<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936dd1bc4982b0e88f9773bd183569158922e7f1","tid":589651,"uid":69217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90ccf9c7e01855dd6ac966efb601ed61d3d0dbb4","tid":589651,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T20:20:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都分享下自己心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只限記敘<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n希望你地唔會tldr<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打好有心<br />\n利伸 睇曬"},{"pid":"1022f887934115a5cded3397bf7320f40f0d4e9e","tid":589651,"uid":69217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T02:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0863cf49117028dac4